nodes.text: The Skaak Tipper Bunker was an underground facility located a short distance west of the Gungan Sacred Place in the Lasay Swamp on the Mid Rim world of Naboo used by the Skaak Tippers during the time of the Galactic Civil War. Sometime following the Battle of Yavin in 0 BBY, Boss Rugor Nass sent a spacer to the bunker to retrieve a Gungan artifact stolen by the Skaak Tippers. Several Skaak Tippers, including Tomi Skaak were killed.
The Skaak Tipper Bunker was a location in the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, prior to the game's closure on December 15, 2011.
